OL,3,CResidents asked to 'pay for service
OL,4,Cyou hope never to use'
OL,6,FResidents in Guernsey, Sark and Herm
OL,7,Fare being urged to take out annual
OL,8,Fambulance cover or risk paying up to
OL,9,Fthousands of pounds in medical bills.
OL,11,FThe subscription costs #71 a year or
OL,12,F#50 for senior citizens but only one
OL,13,Fin ten have it, meaning more than a
OL,14,Fquarter of people who needed the
OL,15,Fservice in 2024 were not protected
OL,16,Ffrom much higher fees.
