OL,3,CResidents asked to 'pay for service
OL,4,Cyou hope never to use'
OL,6,F"We would really encourage younger
OL,7,Fpeople to think about their
OL,8,Fhealthcare. It's never at the
OL,9,Fforefront of your mind. When you're
OL,10,Fyoung, you feel invincible.
OL,12,F"I see too often that life can change
OL,13,Fin the blink of an eye and the last
OL,14,Fthing we want is family to be faced
OL,15,Fwith huge medical bills."
