OL,3,CResidents asked to 'pay for service
OL,4,Cyou hope never to use'
OL,6,FSt John Ambulance and Rescue Service
OL,7,Fis contracted by the States of
OL,8,FGuernsey to provide cover, with its
OL,9,Ffunding split between government
OL,10,Fcontributions, subscriptions, charges
OL,11,Fand donations.
OL,13,FCosts have gone up in recent years due
OL,14,Fto several factors, including higher
OL,15,Ffuel bills and staff salaries.
OL,17,FIt responds to around 7,000 emergency
OL,18,Fcalls and 3,000 non-urgent transfers
OL,19,Facross the Bailiwick each year.
